      "writtenOn": "2014-01-10T22:52:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Normally you would use 0xffffffff as initial for crc_32() (this is also mentioned by the comment for crc_32(), but it doesn\u0027t matter.",
      "revId": "fd3c0ff7dbb759199c23efc1e246176ad93aabd0",
      "serverId": "583131e1-1a33-4f2b-b8ec-82434880f207",
